1.java remote debug
  Scenario_1 : Eclipse as client, remote as server, add the following vm arguments to server jvm startup script.
              -Xdebug -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,address=9999,server=y,suspend=n
  Scenario_2 : remote debug tomcat
              https://confluence.sakaiproject.org/display/BOOT/Setting+Up+Tomcat+For+Remote+Debugging
              https://confluence.sakaiproject.org/display/BOOT/Debugging+Tomcat+Remotely+Using+Eclipse
2. Eclipse 2 debug modes.
   http://blog.csdn.net/lishengc/article/details/6615826
